<% if @reason == :admin_provisioned %>
Welcome aboard!

Our team just finished creating your TechFlash account for <%= @user.email %>.

Click the link below to get started. You'll set a secure password (at least 6 characters, with uppercase, lowercase, a number, and a special character). Link expires in 72 hours.

<%= @reset_url %>

<% if @user.company? %>
After you sign in, you'll land on your dashboard where you can post a job and hire technicians.
<% elsif @user.technician? %>
After you sign in, browse open jobs and claim work that fits your skills.
<% end %>
<% else %>
Reset your TechFlash password

We received a request to reset the password for <%= @user.email %>.

If you did not ask for this, ignore this email.

Open this link to set a new password (expires in 72 hours):
<%= @reset_url %>
<% end %>
